# Technical Specifications
.pull-left[
.panelset[
.panel[.panel-name[Orbit]

Type: Sun-synchronous

Altitude: 705 km (438 miles)

Inclination: 98.2°

Global Revisit: 16 days (8 days with L8)
]

.panel[.panel-name[Sensors]

OLI-2: Operational Land Imager 2 (9 spectral bands)

TIRS-2: Thermal Infrared Sensor 2 (2 thermal bands)

Swath Width: 185 km
]
]
]

